Bvw originated from the global developer community. We are committed to using the most advanced blockchain technology to bring new thinking and practical inspiration to the application of blockchain. Any operation and technology of bvw represents a kind of social experiment of technology. Please participate carefully. As the attitude and policies of the world is major countries on digital currency transactions and blockchain projects are not clear, bvw will strictly abide by the relevant laws of the world on digital assets and make the following statement.
Bvw will not provide use to the following countries and regions: the United States, mainland China, Hong Kong, North Korea, Cuba, Iran, Bangladesh, Malaysia, Syria, Bolivia, etc.
Bvw is a completely decentralized application, unable to effectively conduct KYC certification audit. During the operation period, users in the above countries should consciously delete and exit.
